data.description: This amazing home has 4 Bedrooms + Den and 4 baths . Take your next adventure into this home and experience your next oasis in living. Take the step towards beauty and luxury, safety and security, and memories that will last more than a life time. You'll find the right space, in the right places, in Driftwood Model. On the first floor, an airy kitchen with island dovetails with a cafe area and gathering room, while a room off the kitchen multitasks as a den or home office. An impressive staircase leads to a go-to space for making family memories.
